ACCELEROMETER_ALGORITHM There are two possible modes of operation of the accelerometer algorithm: Activity or Tailbeat.
ACCELEROMETER_SAMPLES_PER_SECOND Number of acceleration samples taken on each axis per second. Sampling rate can be 5 Hertz (5 measurements/s) or 10 Hertz (10 measurements/s).
